      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Honest value on the table \u2014 this vehicle is in fair condition and priced accordingly! It's a functional, drivable car that gets the job done, though it does show its age with some visible wear on the exterior and interior that you'd expect at this price point. There may be a few items that could use attention down the road, but overall it runs and drives. If you're looking for reliable transportation at an accessible price and don't mind a little character, this one's worth a look!",
