    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront about what that means before you consider purchasing. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 the paint is faded, scratched, and has visible rust in multiple areas, with several dents and dings throughout the body panels. The interior is similarly worn, with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard surfaces, and non-functional features including climate controls and some electrical components. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention: expect to budget for repairs to get it running reliably. It starts and can be driven, but it is not in a condition we would describe as road-ready without some work. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or seeking parts. We are pricing it accordingly to reflect the honest state of the car, and we encourage any serious buyer to inspect it thoroughly in person before committing.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition \u2014 a solid, reliable used car that has been well cared for but shows the expected signs of normal, everyday use. The exterior presents well overall, with only minor cosmetic blemishes such as light surface scratches or small scuffs consistent with regular driving. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on high-contact areas like the seats and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts significantly from comfort or usability. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, with no major issues to report \u2014 it has been maintained and is ready for daily use. This is a dependable vehicle for a buyer looking for good value without the premium price of a mint-condition car.",
      "price": 34000.0,
