      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a designation that reflects a car that has been genuinely well cared for and is ready for dependable daily use. The exterior presents nicely overall: the paint retains good depth and shine, though a careful eye will find the minor door dings, light surface scratches, and small scuffs that are typical of a vehicle that has seen regular use. There are no significant dents, rust, or structural concerns. The interior is clean and functional \u2014 the seats show modest wear consistent with its age and mileage, the dashboard and trim are intact, and all major controls operate as intended. Mechanically, the car is in solid shape: the engine starts readily, runs smoothly, and delivers consistent performance. The transmission shifts cleanly, brakes are responsive, and the suspension feels stable on the road. Routine maintenance has been kept up, and there are no warning lights or known outstanding issues. This is an honest, capable vehicle that will serve a buyer well without the premium of a mint-condition car \u2014 priced accordingly and ready to go.",
